{
  "id": "5dda5a2347be280017372984",
  "title": "働き方改革の意味",
  "created": 1574591018,
  "updated": 1591870607,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5dda5a2347be280017372984",
      "text": "働き方改革の意味",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574591018,
      "updated": 1574592974
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5a2daff09e0000b00eee",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/5c941a389fcf0c3b881d24abb9bca0d6]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574591021,
      "updated": 1574591022
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda61d4aff09e00002542aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592980,
      "updated": 1574592980
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5a2eaff09e0000b00ef0",
      "text": "[働き方改革]の意味",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574591022,
      "updated": 1574592983
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5a7eaff09e000021ad26",
      "text": "\t[労働時間の短縮]だと思っている人Aと、[働く場所と時間の多様化]だと思っている人Bがいる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574591102,
      "updated": 1574592993
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5a95aff09e000021ad27",
      "text": "\tノー残業デー(強制的な労働時間の短縮)は",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574591125,
      "updated": 1574592133
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5e85aff09e000021ad28",
      "text": "\t\tAにとってはポジティブ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592133,
      "updated": 1591870520
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee20439aff09e0000b17955",
      "text": "\t\t　時間が減るから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870521,
      "updated": 1591870525
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee20436aff09e0000b17954",
      "text": "\t\tBにとってはネガティブ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870518,
      "updated": 1591870518
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee2043eaff09e0000b17956",
      "text": "\t\t　時間の選択肢を奪われるから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870526,
      "updated": 1591870533
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5ea3aff09e000021ad29",
      "text": "\t\t関連: [強制的定時退社も裁量が低い状態]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592163,
      "updated": 1574592185
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5a2eaff09e0000b00eef",
      "text": "\t副業は",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574591022,
      "updated": 1574592205
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5ecdaff09e000021ad2b",
      "text": "\t\tAにとってはネガティブ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592205,
      "updated": 1591870541
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee2044faff09e0000b17957",
      "text": "\t\t　労働時間が増えるので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870544,
      "updated": 1591870545
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5ee9aff09e000021ad2d",
      "text": "\t\tBにとってはポジティブ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592234,
      "updated": 1591870552
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee20459aff09e0000b17958",
      "text": "\t\t　場所と時間の多様化なので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870553,
      "updated": 1591870555
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5ecdaff09e000021ad2a",
      "text": "\t週休3日の強制は",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592205,
      "updated": 1574592260
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5f04aff09e000021ad2f",
      "text": "\t\tこれも強制的な労働時間の短縮なので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592260,
      "updated": 1591870568
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee20464aff09e0000b1795b",
      "text": "\t\t　Aにとってポジティブ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870565,
      "updated": 1591870565
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee20462aff09e0000b1795a",
      "text": "\t\t　Bにとってネガティブ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870563,
      "updated": 1591870563
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5f13aff09e000021ad30",
      "text": "\t同一労働同一賃金",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592276,
      "updated": 1574592366
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5f6aaff09e000021ad32",
      "text": "\t\tこれは厚生労働省が働き方改革だと思っている概念",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592363,
      "updated": 1574592379
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5f65aff09e000021ad31",
      "text": "\t\t\t[同一労働同一賃金 | 働き方改革支援のご案内 | 厚生労働省 https://www.mhlw.go.jp/hatarakikata/same.html]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592361,
      "updated": 1574592380
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee20483aff09e0000b1795c",
      "text": "\t\tAにとってはニュートラル",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870596,
      "updated": 1591870596
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee20487aff09e0000b1795d",
      "text": " \t\t労働時間の短縮にはつながらないので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870600,
      "updated": 1591870601
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee2048baff09e0000b1795e",
      "text": "\t\tBにとってはポジティブ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870604,
      "updated": 1591870604
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee2048daff09e0000b1795f",
      "text": " \t\t非正規雇用の待遇が正規雇用と対等になるのなら、働き方の選択肢が増えるので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591870606,
      "updated": 1591870607
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda5f97aff09e000021ad33",
      "text": "\t\t期待した通りに機能しているかどうかは別の話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592408,
      "updated": 1574592837
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda6144aff09e000021ad38",
      "text": "\t\t\tsee [正社員の手当が消える… 非正規との格差是正へ　　:日本経済新聞 https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXMZO52450760R21C19A1KNTP00/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592837,
      "updated": 1574592838
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda6148aff09e000021ad39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592840,
      "updated": 1574592840
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda60a7aff09e000021ad35",
      "text": "まとめ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592679,
      "updated": 1574593014
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda61f6aff09e00002542ab",
      "text": "\t「働き方改革」は解釈の異なる人が結構いて、逆の結論を導くことがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574593014,
      "updated": 1574593017
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda61f8aff09e00002542ac",
      "text": "\tなので、相手がどういう意味で使っているのかを確認しないと危険な言葉だ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574593017,
      "updated": 1574634969
    },
    {
      "id": "5dda60a8aff09e000021ad36",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574592681,
      "updated": 1574592681
    },
    {
      "id": "5ddf8e7faff09e0000bb7e00",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574932095,
      "updated": 1574932098
    },
    {
      "id": "5ddf8e81aff09e0000bb7e02",
      "text": "\t[15年間で20代人口は7人に1人減る]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574932098,
      "updated": 1574932211
    },
    {
      "id": "5ddf8fe9aff09e0000bb7e06",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1574932459,
      "updated": 1574932459
    }
  ]
}